des:
VoiceBrew's Tip Of The Day flash briefing gives you one awesome thing to try with Alexa every day, delivered in a minute or less.
 
VoiceBrew's mission is to help people get more out of Alexa. VoiceBrew sends 30,000+ subscribers a free daily email newsletter with one actually awesome use for Alexa. Sign up at voicebrew.com!
 
This skill was designed, developed, and is hosted by Witlingo. If you would like your very own flash briefing, send an email to contact@witlingo.com
